```flow
st=>start: user request
op=>condition: cache 
cond=>operation: cache > db
push=>operation: push
up=>operation: update db

db=>operation:select db
update=>operation:update cache

st->op->cond->push->up
op->db->update->push

op(yes)->cond
op(no)->db-

```

